4K8.F.summary: Kamux Oyj engages in the retail and wholesale of used cars and integrated services consumer and corporate customers. As of December 31, 2020, it operated 50 showrooms in Finland; 20 showrooms in Sweden; and 8 showrooms in Germany, as well as an online store. It also offers financing and insurance products; and sells used cars in auctions. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in HÃ¤meenlinna, Finland.
